features: Expandable Large Capacity: Our pencil case can store up to 100+ pens or pencils. With the expandable special design, you can simply unzip the case to extend its height, providing extra room for all your writing essentials. Farewell cluttered spaces!

Built to Last: Our aesthetic pencil case is crafted from high-quality waterproof nylon, ensuring durability and protection for your stationery. With smooth zipper, designed for frequent use without any snags or sticking, you'll find opening and closing a breeze. Perfect for everyday use.

Compact & Portable: Size 4.13*8.66in(W*L), Our nylon pencil case with zip offers ample storage for all your stationery needs. Lightweight and portable, it's perfect for on-the-go use. Say goodbye to cluttered desks and lost pens, organization becomes effortless, and learning becomes a breeze.

5 Compartments: The pencil case organiser has 5 compartments, which are easy to classify, keeping your writing tools well organized. one front zipper pocket, one mesh pocket for important items, five pen slots, and a large main compartment. Enough to hold all of a student's stationery.

Multi-function: This large pencil case is not only for pencils, it also can meet practical needs for different people such as makeup brush bag, craft pouch, travel or make up bag, 3C products or accessories bag.

Thoughtful Back-to-School Present: Whether it's for your son, daughter, or any student returning to school, our pencil bag is a thoughtful and practical present. It's sure to bring joy and make their school days a little brighter! Please note that this product is not suitable for children under 12 years old.
